data.description: Welcome to Terrace View! Wonderful townhome community minutes  from Lakeland Hills amenities and Hwy 167 for commutes, comfortable  living area boasts soaring 9ft ceilings and gas fireplace. Master  bedroom is accompanied by a 5-piece master bath & nicely-sized walk-in  closet. Convenient upstairs laundry. Non conforming bonus room in  garage. Remodeled kitchen counters, upstairs flooring, and bathroom tiles  in 2020. Low HOA dues. No sign per seller request.
